-- MOVES-BNY Mellon names Taiber as country executive for Germany 
-- 
-- Tue Jul 01, 2014 06:17AM EDT
-- None



July 1 (Reuters) - Investment management company BNY Mellon appointed Werner Taiber as country executive for Germany.

Taiber will remain chief executive of Meriten Investment Management, a specialist investment boutique of BNY Mellon, the company said.